OL,3,CDumfries & Galloway Police focus on
OL,4,Cpoor driving as rider caught taking
OL,5,Cselfie
OL,7,FA motorcyclist who was caught taking a
OL,8,Fselfie on the hard shoulder of a
OL,9,Fmotorway told police officers he "just
OL,10,Fwanted to telephone".
OL,12,FThe rider was given a warning by the
OL,13,FDumfries and Galloway officers, who
OL,14,Fare cracking down on poor driving
OL,15,Fhabits as part of a national campaign
OL,16,Fto prevent fatal road accidents.
OL,18,FThe Fatal Five refers to the five most
OL,19,Fcommon offending behaviours that
OL,20,Fcontribute to serious road crashes and
OL,21,Ffatalities.
