OL,3,CDumfries & Galloway Police focus on
OL,4,Cpoor driving as rider caught taking
OL,5,Cselfie
OL,7,FThe five main behaviours targeted are:
OL,8,Fspeeding, drink and drug driving,
OL,9,Fmobile phone use, careless driving and
OL,10,Fnot wearing a seatbelt.
OL,12,FAccording to Transport Scotland,
OL,13,Fduring the campaign in April 2024,
OL,14,FPolice Scotland and safety camera
OL,15,Funits detected over 1000 offences
OL,16,Frelating to those behaviours.
OL,18,FThe roads policing team in Dumfries
OL,19,Fand Galloway are responsible for
OL,20,Fcovering 4000 miles of roads.
