OL,5,Cselfie
OL,7,FAs the area is one of Scotland's more
OL,8,Frural and sparsely populated regions,
OL,9,Fit poses more road safety challenges
OL,10,Flike long roads, single carriageways
OL,11,Fand sometimes more difficult weather
OL,12,Fand visibility conditions.
OL,14,FThese, paired with poor driving
OL,15,Fhabits, can have fatal consequences.
OL,17,FReporter Natalie Higgins joined police
OL,18,Fon a patrol targeting people with poor
OL,19,Fdriving habits:
