OL,4,Cpoor driving as rider caught taking
OL,5,Cselfie
OL,7,FIt's a sunny morning in Lockerbie and
OL,8,FPC Lawrence Nelson and PC Alan Dickson
OL,9,Fare feeling positive about their
OL,10,Fupcoming shift.
OL,12,FWithin five minutes of joining them in
OL,13,Ftheir unmarked patrol car, they spot a
OL,14,Fvan driver using his phone behind the
OL,15,Fwheel.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
