OL,4,Cpoor driving as rider caught taking
OL,5,Cselfie
OL,7,FThe driver is pulled over and asked
OL,8,Fwhy he felt the need to use his phone
OL,9,Fwhile driving. He was apologetic and
OL,10,Funderstood why he had been pulled
OL,11,Fover, but understandably looked
OL,12,Ffrustrated with himself when told he
OL,13,Fwould be hit with six points on his
OL,14,Flicence and a #200 fine.
OL,16,FPC Dickson, who is in the driving seat
OL,17,Ffor the shift, tells me how the man
OL,18,Freacted:
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/11
