OL,4,Cpoor driving as rider caught taking
OL,5,Cselfie
OL,7,F"He's been apologetic, he's admitted
OL,8,Fusing his device. We explained to him
OL,9,Fwhat the implications are using it and
OL,10,Fthat you're four times more likely to
OL,11,Fbe involved in a crash when you're
OL,12,Fusing your phone whilst driving and
OL,13,Fnow he's been issued a conditional
OL,14,Ffixed penalty notice."
OL,16,FAs we move onto the A74, PC Nelson
OL,17,Fspots a driver so engrossed on his
OL,18,Fphone he nearly crashes into the back
OL,19,Fof the patrol car.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/11
