OL,3,CDumfries & Galloway Police focus on
OL,4,Cpoor driving as rider caught taking
OL,5,Cselfie
OL,7,F"I've seen him put it down by his
OL,8,Fright side," PC Nelson said.
OL,10,F"He's not even looking at the road
OL,11,Fbecause he's not looking at me,
OL,12,Fbecause he'd be able to see me looking
OL,13,Fat him. Then he's still weaving about
OL,14,Fthese lanes.
OL,16,F"He's not paying attention to what
OL,17,Fhe's doing because he can't see me
OL,18,Fstaring at him through the back of a
OL,19,Fcar, it's certainly careless driving."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/11
