OL,3,CDumfries & Galloway Police focus on
OL,4,Cpoor driving as rider caught taking
OL,5,Cselfie
OL,7,FThe two officers are part of a team
OL,8,Fthat covers the 2400sqm across
OL,9,FDumfries and Galloway.
OL,11,FThey aim to keep the roads safe by
OL,12,Fenforcing traffic laws, investigating
OL,13,Fcollisions, disrupting criminal
OL,14,Factivity, and educating the public on
OL,15,Froad safety.
OL,17,FThey respond to incidents, manage
OL,18,Fpursuits, collect evidence, and work
OL,19,Fwith other agencies to ensure road
OL,20,Fusers follow the law and to prevent
OL,21,Finjuries and fatalities.
