OL,4,Cpoor driving as rider caught taking
OL,5,Cselfie
OL,7,FBack on the roads and it doesn't take
OL,8,Flong for PC Nelson to spot another
OL,9,Fcareless driver - a motorcyclist who
OL,10,Fhas pulled onto the hard shoulder to
OL,11,Ftake a selfie.
OL,13,FHe tells the rider: "This spot is for
OL,14,Femergencies. What could happen is a
OL,15,Florry driver could come along, be
OL,16,Fdistracted, swerve into the hard
OL,17,Fshoulder then hit and kill you."
OL,19,FThe rider's response: "I just wanted
OL,20,Fto telephone".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/11
