OL,4,Cpoor driving as rider caught taking
OL,5,Cselfie
OL,7,FPC Nelson joins us back in the car,
OL,8,Fadding: "When you get a distracted or
OL,9,Ftired driver, he will drift out the
OL,10,Flane and you can imagine they won't be
OL,11,Faware of him until the collide with
OL,12,Fhim and then it's catastrophic.
OL,13,FStopping in the hard shoulder is just
OL,14,Fnot a safe place to be."
OL,16,FPolice are carrying out increased
OL,17,Fpatrols on priority routes,
OL,18,Fparticularly where previous fatal
OL,19,Fcrashes have occurred, with an aim to
OL,20,Fcurb risky driving behaviours.
